{"tid":1065941,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我能否變成淤泥 再一次沾染你","createTime":"2019-03-17T15:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T07:44:29.000Z","uid":182558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3d53c98a6d43bab62d59a0b7a007576974a3778f","tid":1065941,"uid":182558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T15:22:38.000Z","msg":"我多想再見你 哪怕匆匆一眼就別離<br />\n<br />\n往往無情的 往往有深意<br />\n故意視而不見 再故意相遇<br />\n往往深情的 往往無心<br />\n我擁著一段叫遺憾的過去<br />\n<br />\n也許你也忐忑<br />\n也許你也失落<br />\n也許你也背著我喝了一杯酒<br />\n也許你也困惑<br />\n也許你也不懂<br />\n可是最美不過那夜和你看過的星空<br />\n<br />\n如果你也相信<br />\n如果你也堅定<br />\n如果你也不在意流言與蜚語<br />\n如果你也願意<br />\n如果你也可以<br />\n等我們老了以後 就定居在這裡<br />\n<br />\n總有些遺憾要學會放下<br />\n前路不需太重的行囊<br />\n和過去 和解吧<br />\n<br />\n也許曾經的故事已經不必放心上<br />\n走過的路也可以忘<br />\n今後我所有的牽掛<br />\n所有的嚮往<br />\n都和你一樣"},{"pid":"65bbbc81b0a81ba92e918106da6b1ff6d2643984","tid":1065941,"uid":11989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T15:24:10.000Z","msg":"房東的貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3cec3b155a235785917917c57726185064ff766","tid":1065941,"uid":182558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65bbbc81b0a81ba92e918106da6b1ff6d2643984","tid":1065941,"uid":11989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T15:24:10.000Z","msg":"房東的貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T15:24:51.000Z","msg":"聽咗成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aad89c9ffe2f9caa0f6d5c04f85a0464b0c9d13","tid":1065941,"uid":206363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T15:56:25.000Z","msg":"我而家都聽梗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a621cd176a32611bdb3af8c9db98a61ec8edc64a","tid":1065941,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T15:57:09.000Z","msg":"房東的喵"},{"pid":"0673d6f675fe8b6ab52ac0df384bdfecd853129c